{"title":"Augusta, GA — Cost of Living, Housing & Relocation Guide [2026]","description":"Complete guide to Augusta, GA: cost of living, home prices, neighborhoods, remote work readiness, and relocation tips.","url":"https://urcity.com/cities/augusta-ga/","content":"\u003ch2 id=\"overview\"\u003eOverview\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAugusta is a city in GA with a population of 202,081. Home of the Masters with cheap housing, the Savannah River, and Southern charm.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"cost-of-living\"\u003eCost of Living\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAugusta\u0026rsquo;s cost of living index is 90.5 (US average = 100).\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ctable\u003e\n\t\u003cthead\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003ctr\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003cth\u003eCategory\u003c/th\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003cth\u003eAugusta\u003c/th\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003cth\u003eNational Average\u003c/th\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003cth\u003eDifference\u003c/th\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003c/tr\u003e\n\t\u003c/thead\u003e\n\t\u003ctbody\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003ctr\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003eOverall\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e90.5\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e100\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e-9.5%\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003c/tr\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003ctr\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003eHousing\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e78.5\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e100\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e-21.5%\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003c/tr\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003ctr\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003eUtilities\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e98.5\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e100\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e-1.5%\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003c/tr\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003ctr\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003eGroceries\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e96.8\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e100\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e-3.2%\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003c/tr\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003ctr\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003eTransportation\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e104.2\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e100\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e+4.2%\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003c/tr\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003ctr\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003eHealthcare\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e100.5\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e100\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e+0.5%\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003c/tr\u003e\n\t\u003c/tbody\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eData source: Council for Community and Economic Research (C2ER), 2026\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"housing-market\"\u003eHousing Market\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003ctable\u003e\n\t\u003cthead\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003ctr\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003cth\u003eMetric\u003c/th\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003cth\u003eValue\u003c/th\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003c/tr\u003e\n\t\u003c/thead\u003e\n\t\u003ctbody\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003ctr\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003eMedian Home Price\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e$165,000\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003c/tr\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003ctr\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003eMedian Rent (1BR)\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e$1050/month\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003c/tr\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003ctr\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003eMedian Rent (2BR)\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e$1,312/month\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003c/tr\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003ctr\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003ePrice per Sq Ft\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e$110\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003c/tr\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003ctr\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003eYear-over-Year Change\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e-1.0%\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003c/tr\u003e\n\t\u003c/tbody\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eData source: Zillow Research, May 2026\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"true-cost-of-home-ownership\"\u003eTrue Cost of Home Ownership\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"calculator-widget\" id=\"home-calc\"\u003e\n  \u003ch3\u003eTrue Cost of Home Ownership\u003c/h3\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"calc-row\"\u003e\n    \u003clabel\u003eHome Price ($)\u003c/label\u003e\n    \u003cinput type=\"number\" id=\"home-price\" value=\"450000\" min=\"0\" step=\"10000\"\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"calc-row\"\u003e\n    \u003clabel\u003eDown Payment (%)\u003c/label\u003e\n    \u003cinput type=\"number\" id=\"down-payment\" value=\"20\" min=\"0\" max=\"100\" step=\"5\"\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"calc-row\"\u003e\n    \u003clabel\u003eInterest Rate (%)\u003c/label\u003e\n    \u003cinput type=\"number\" id=\"interest-rate\" value=\"6.5\" min=\"0\" max=\"20\" step=\"0.1\"\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"calc-row\"\u003e\n    \u003clabel\u003eProperty Tax Rate (%)\u003c/label\u003e\n    \u003cinput type=\"number\" id=\"tax-rate\" value=\"1.8\" min=\"0\" max=\"5\" step=\"0.1\"\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"calc-row\"\u003e\n    \u003clabel\u003eHOA/Month ($)\u003c/label\u003e\n    \u003cinput type=\"number\" id=\"hoa\" value=\"0\" min=\"0\" step=\"50\"\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cbutton class=\"btn btn-primary\" onclick=\"calculateHome()\"\u003eCalculate\u003c/button\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"calc-result\" id=\"home-result\" style=\"display:none;\"\u003e\n    \u003ch4\u003eMonthly Costs\u003c/h4\u003e\n    \u003cul\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003eMortgage: \u003cstrong id=\"mortgage-payment\"\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003eProperty Tax: \u003cstrong id=\"tax-payment\"\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003eInsurance: \u003cstrong id=\"insurance-payment\"\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003eHOA: \u003cstrong id=\"hoa-payment\"\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli class=\"total\"\u003eTotal Monthly: \u003cstrong id=\"total-monthly\"\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\n    \u003ch4\u003eTotal Cost Over 30 Years\u003c/h4\u003e\n    \u003cp id=\"total-cost\"\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cscript\u003e\nfunction calculateHome() {\n  const price = parseFloat(document.getElementById('home-price').value);\n  const downPercent = parseFloat(document.getElementById('down-payment').value);\n  const rate = parseFloat(document.getElementById('interest-rate').value);\n  const taxRate = parseFloat(document.getElementById('tax-rate').value);\n  const hoa = parseFloat(document.getElementById('hoa').value);\n  \n  const downPayment = price * (downPercent / 100);\n  const loanAmount = price - downPayment;\n  const monthlyRate = rate / 100 / 12;\n  const numPayments = 30 * 12;\n  \n  const mortgage = loanAmount * (monthlyRate * Math.pow(1 + monthlyRate, numPayments)) / (Math.pow(1 + monthlyRate, numPayments) - 1);\n  const tax = (price * (taxRate / 100)) / 12;\n  const insurance = (price * 0.0035) / 12;\n  const total = mortgage + tax + insurance + hoa;\n  \n  const totalCost = (total * numPayments) + downPayment;\n  \n  document.getElementById('mortgage-payment').textContent = '$' + Math.round(mortgage).toLocaleString();\n  document.getElementById('tax-payment').textContent = '$' + Math.round(tax).toLocaleString();\n  document.getElementById('insurance-payment').textContent = '$' + Math.round(insurance).toLocaleString();\n  document.getElementById('hoa-payment').textContent = '$' + Math.round(hoa).toLocaleString();\n  document.getElementById('total-monthly').textContent = '$' + Math.round(total).toLocaleString();\n  document.getElementById('total-cost').textContent = 'You will pay $' + Math.round(totalCost).toLocaleString() + ' over 30 years ($' + price.toLocaleString() + ' home price + $' + Math.round(totalCost - price).toLocaleString() + ' in interest, taxes, and fees).';\n  \n  document.getElementById('home-result').style.display = 'block';\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"best-neighborhoods\"\u003eBest Neighborhoods\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"downtown-augusta\"\u003eDowntown Augusta\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe heart of the city with restaurants, shops, and entertainment. Average rent: $1,260/month.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"augusta-heights\"\u003eAugusta Heights\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTrendy area with local businesses and a mix of historic and modern housing. Average rent: $1,155/month.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"east-augusta\"\u003eEast Augusta\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eUp-and-coming neighborhood with new developments and young professionals. Average rent: $945/month.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"west-augusta\"\u003eWest Augusta\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFamily-friendly area with parks and good schools. Average rent: $997/month.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"remote-work-score\"\u003eRemote Work Score\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAugusta scores 124/100 for remote work readiness:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eInternet Speed:\u003c/strong\u003e Average 200 Mbps (Good)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCoworking Spaces:\u003c/strong\u003e 15+ locations (Good)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCost of Living:\u003c/strong\u003e Moderate (Good)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eClimate:\u003c/strong\u003e 218 sunny days/year (Good)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eQuality of Life:\u003c/strong\u003e High (Good)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"climate\"\u003eClimate\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAugusta has a varied climate with distinct seasons.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ctable\u003e\n\t\u003cthead\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003ctr\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003cth\u003eMonth\u003c/th\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003cth\u003eAvg High\u003c/th\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003cth\u003eAvg Low\u003c/th\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003cth\u003eRainfall\u003c/th\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003c/tr\u003e\n\t\u003c/thead\u003e\n\t\u003ctbody\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003ctr\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003eJanuary\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e54°F\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e34°F\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e2.5\u0026quot;\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003c/tr\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003ctr\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003eApril\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e77°F\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e49°F\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e2.8\u0026quot;\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003c/tr\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003ctr\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003eJuly\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e92°F\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e67°F\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e1.5\u0026quot;\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003c/tr\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003ctr\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003eOctober\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e72°F\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e52°F\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e2.2\u0026quot;\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003c/tr\u003e\n\t\u003c/tbody\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"taxes\"\u003eTaxes\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eState Income Tax:\u003c/strong\u003e 5.75%\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSales Tax:\u003c/strong\u003e 8.0%\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eProperty Tax:\u003c/strong\u003e ~0.8% of assessed value\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"economy\"\u003eEconomy\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMajor industries include technology, healthcare, education, and manufacturing. The unemployment rate is 3.8%.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"faq\"\u003eFAQ\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"faq-section\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/FAQPage\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"faq-item\" itemscope itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\"\u003e\n    \u003ch3 itemprop=\"name\"\u003eIs augusta-ga a good place to live?\u003c/h3\u003e\n    \u003cdiv itemscope itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"\u003e\n      \u003cdiv itemprop=\"text\"\u003e\n        \u003cp\u003eaugusta-ga offers a strong combination of affordability, job opportunities, and quality of life. Use our cost of living calculator and relocation guides to see if it fits your budget and lifestyle.\u003c/p\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"faq-item\" itemscope itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\"\u003e\n    \u003ch3 itemprop=\"name\"\u003eWhat is the cost of living in augusta-ga?\u003c/h3\u003e\n    \u003cdiv itemscope itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"\u003e\n      \u003cdiv itemprop=\"text\"\u003e\n        \u003cp\u003eThe cost of living in augusta-ga varies by neighborhood and lifestyle. Check our detailed cost breakdown above for specific numbers on housing, groceries, utilities, and transportation.\u003c/p\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"faq-item\" itemscope itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\"\u003e\n    \u003ch3 itemprop=\"name\"\u003eHow much do I need to earn to live comfortably in augusta-ga?\u003c/h3\u003e\n    \u003cdiv itemscope itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"\u003e\n      \u003cdiv itemprop=\"text\"\u003e\n        \u003cp\u003eUse our \u003ca href=\"/tools/salary-equivalence-calculator/\"\u003eSalary Equivalence Calculator\u003c/a\u003e to find out how much you need to earn in augusta-ga to maintain your current standard of living.\u003c/p\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"data-sources\"\u003eData Sources\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCost of living: Council for Community and Economic Research (C2ER)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eHousing data: Zillow Research\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDemographics: US Census Bureau\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eClimate: National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration (NOAA)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTaxes: Tax Foundation\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eLast updated: June 28, 2026\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n"}